Package: ParallelPC
Type: Package
Title: Paralellised Versions of Constraint Based Causal Discovery
        Algorithms
Version: 1.2
Date: 2015-10-30
Author: Thuc Duy Le, Tao Hoang, Shu Hu, and Liang Zhang
Maintainer: Thuc Duy Le <Thuc.Le@unisa.edu.au>
Imports: methods
Suggests: bnlearn, pcalg, parallel, Rgraphviz
Description: Parallelise constraint based causality discovery and
        causal inference methods. The parallelised algorithms in the
        package will generate the same results as that of the 'pcalg'
        package but will be much more efficient.
